Package: trdp-simulator
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libssl3, libtinyxml2-9, nlohmann-json3-dev, libdrogon-dev
Description: TRDP simulator with HTTP API, PD/MD controls, and diagnostics
 This package installs the TRDP simulator daemon, its systemd unit,
 sample configuration, and default environment overrides.
